{"about_the_game":"Zra Stories is a story-driven exploration game that combines adventure with crime story elements. Play a young nature caretaker \u2013 a sorceress with an ability to control natural phenomena and restore flora with her special spells. A routine order turns into a full-fledged investigation when the heroine tries to uncover the reason for the desolation of the island of Zra.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Try yourself as a nature caretaker</u></h2>Use magic and spells to control the wind, create rain and lightning. Restore the flora of the devastated island.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Reveal the local residents\u2019 secrets</u></h2>Conduct an investigation and find the reason for the desolation of the once flourishing island.<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Explore an interesting and picturesque world</u></h2>Go on an adventure through the game world to learn about the unusual features of the local nature and find secret places.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1724994615","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572820/page.bg.jpg?t=1724994615","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572820/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1724994615","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572820/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1724994615","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Zra Stories is a story-driven exploration game that combines adventure with crime story elements. Play a young nature caretaker \u2013 a sorceress with an ability to control natural phenomena and restore flor